@node "LEMMINGS 2 - THE TRIBES"
LEMMINGS 2 - THE TRIBES

This cheat will allow you to select any level for any tribe.  Go to each
corner of the menu screen and press BOTH mouse buttons each time until you
hear a lemming faintly squeal "Let's Go".  You should hear this at each point
of pressing the mouse buttons.  Now you can select any level on any tribe and
have 60 lemmings on each, which means that you only have to complete the last
level of each tribe to complete the game.
@endnode
@node "LEONARDO"
LEONARDO

Here are several game level passwords:

   EMMENTALER for level 10
   ALPHORN for 20
   MATTERHORN for 30
   IVANHOE for level ?
   FREIBIERC for infinite lives.  The screen will flash and it will tell you
             that you have discovered the secret.
@endnode
@node "LETHAL WEAPON"
LETHAL WEAPON

During play, hold down any of the following simultaneously:

         'ALT', 'Y' and 'I' to turn off sprite collision
         'ALT', 'Y' and 'K' to increase ammo.
         'ALT', 'Y' and 'l' to increase lives.
         'ALT', 'Y' and 'M' to remove game sprites and platforms.
         'ALT', 'Y' and 'N' to correct game sprites and platforms.
         'ALT', 'Y' and 'Q' to get game completion credits.
         'ALT', 'Y' and any number from '0' to '9' to select the levels.

If you jump onto the notice board next to the Mission 1 entrance and push up,
you'll be able to collect 4 extra lives.

On mission 3, jump along the 4th platform, jump up and keep pushing up and
you'll climb the wall.  When you reach the top, walk to the left and keep
going until you reach the edge of the screen.  There you will find 10
magnifying glasses, one gun, a round of bullets and an extra life.

The various level codes are;

    1. KUIRFR        1. KSIIFL
    2. BEIGCF    or  2. ECYOIR   (2nd set Amiga Power Magazine)
    3. RSRKBA        3. FLRSKB
    4. LYLSUA        4. UEOASF
@endnode
@node "LETHAL XCESS"
LETHAL XCESS

In the Options-Menu, enter the word "coke".  When the screen flashes blue,
you are in the cheat mode.  Now press: 'F1' for Triangle, 'F2' for Drones,
'F3' for Alienwiper, 'F4' for Blaster, 'F5' for Laser, 'F6' for Formation,
'F7' for Seeker, 'F8' for Hunter, and 'F9' for Shield.
@endnode
@node "LICENSE TO KILL"
LICENSE TO KILL

Use 'F8' as a levelskipper.
@endnode
@node "LIGHT CORRIDOR"
LIGHT CORRIDOR

