@node "LINE OF FIRE"
LINE OF FIRE

Type in "OPERATION FERRET" on the control options screen.  You should now be
invincible and pressing keys '0'-'9' will allow you to skip levels.  You
could also try pressing the 'HELP' key once the game has loaded for a secret
message and then type in "WHAT A BUMMER" for infinite credits and the level
skip.
@endnode
@node "LIONHEART"
LIONHEART

Pull down on the joystick then press 'P' to pause the game while still in the
crouched position.  Use the following keys:

 'F1-F10' -          Level select.
 '1-5' -             More level select.
 'RETURN' -          Shake the ground.
 'S' -               Plays sound.
 'UP CURSOR KEY' -   Sound minus 1.
 'DOWN CURSOR KEY' - Sound plus 1.
 'D' -               Die.
 'HELP' -            Toggle one and two button joystick.
 'M' -               Toggle sound.
 'SPACE' -           Not really sure.
 'CTRL' -            Invincibility and you can move the guy anywhere using
the mouse.  When you have him in the desired position press 'CTRL' again to
release him.  The right mouse button also acts as a pause.
@endnode
@node "LITTLE PUFF"
LITTLE PUFF

Type in "FAT DRAGON NINJA" then 'Capslock' + the 'L' key will skip levels.
@endnode
