@node "LOTUS ESPRIT TURBO CHALLENGE"
LOTUS ESPRIT TURBO CHALLENGE

During a two player game type player one's name as "FIELDS OF FIRE" and
player two's as "IN A BIG COUNTRY".  This eliminates the lead to qualify in
the Top Ten and allows you to crawl around the track at a much safer speed.
If this doesn't work, try reversing the names of the two players.

Try player's names as "MONSTER" and "SEVENTEEN" for an especially rocky ride
in a vertically scrolling shoot-em-up.
@endnode
@node "LOTUS TURBO CHALLENGE II"
LOTUS TURBO CHALLENGE II

Typing the password: "TURPENTINE", shuts the timer off at 10, and typing
"DEESIDE" allows you to qualify regardless of your effort.

Type "DUX" as a password to play a small sub-game.

If you enter the words "MONSTER" and "SEVENTEEN" (in the respective name
slots), you'll discover a rather familiar game.

